race.comment: FROM THE DISCO (5) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 318m behind Elusive Tom (19.16) in a Grade 4/5. Key runner on her best form. LYDIA WAVE (7) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Richmond over 320m (18.47). Has ability and can atone. COCO CARGO (1) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at this track over 318m behind Midnight Mack (19.17) in a Mix 3/4. Bold showing expected. DEVOTIONAL (4) cannot be left out after placing last start.
